OL,3,C'We're healthy and we can't pass it
OL,4,Con' - HIV patient's message to combat
OL,5,Cstigma
OL,7,FShe is now backing a charity campaign
OL,8,Fwhich aims to stop the stigma, as she
OL,9,Fwants people to understand that the
OL,10,Ftreatment is effective at making sure
OL,11,Fshe is not able to pass on HIV to
OL,12,Fanyone else.
OL,14,FMs Hunter said: "I didn't have the
OL,15,Fcorrect information and that caused me
OL,16,Fto have fear, the fear that I was
OL,17,Fgoing to die.
OL,19,F"Obviously, I got that information
OL,20,Fthat allowed me to tell myself that I
OL,21,Fcan live a long and healthy life."
