OL,3,C'We're healthy and we can't pass it
OL,4,Con' - HIV patient's message to combat
OL,5,Cstigma
OL,7,FWhen asked how it makes her feel when
OL,8,Fpeople are judgemental about her
OL,9,Fdiagnosis, she said: "It makes me feel
OL,10,Fdifferent, it makes me feel
OL,11,Finadequate, it makes me feel as though
OL,12,FI've done something wrong.
OL,14,F"There was a potential partner and I
OL,15,Ftold him I was living with HIV, on
OL,16,Fmedication, and he told me 'I value my
OL,17,Flife too much to have a relationship
OL,18,Fwith you'."
