OL,3,C'We're healthy and we can't pass it
OL,4,Con' - HIV patient's message to combat
OL,5,Cstigma
OL,7,FShe wants to combat the stigma of HIV
OL,8,Fpatients like her, saying "We're here,
OL,9,Fwe're great, we're living a healthy
OL,10,Flife, we can't pass HIV on. Please
OL,11,Flook at the science."
OL,13,FMs Hunter is one of than 100,000
OL,14,Fpeople thought to be living with the
OL,15,Fvirus in the UK.
OL,17,FThe 'Can't Pass It On' message, is
OL,18,Fbeing shared across Brighton and Hove
OL,19,Fas part of an awareness drive by the
OL,20,FTerrance Higgins Trust.
