OL,5,Cstigma
OL,7,FMarc Tweed from Terrance Higgins
OL,8,FTrust, said: "People have got really
OL,9,Fout of date ideas about HIV.
OL,11,F"They don't realise how far HIV
OL,12,Ftreatment has progressed and for most
OL,13,Fpeople that means one pill a day.
OL,14,FThere's even injectable HIV
OL,15,Fmedication, some people have an
OL,16,Finjection once every six months."
